title: Robbie Maddison
description:
Robbie Maddison is a freestyle motocross innovator, world record holder and an all around nice guy to boot. 

Hailing from down under, Maddo is always having fun on his bike, even as he progresses FMX to the next level. Give a quick search online to check out some of his sick feats from the last few Red Bull New Years Eve events and you'll see what we mean. 

Maddo's rocking our Series 3MX motocross goggles when he's on the bike and our A.C.E.S. gear when he's chilling.

Stay connected with Maddo and our FMX program online at www.arnette.com
